@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yauwnb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.21 / ((tmp + 0.29 + v1 + 0.77) - (v0 + 0.57 - v1 + 0.90)))
    v0 = (v1 + wp.exp(0.46))
    v2 = 0.94
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.66)) + wp.cos((tmp + 0.19 + v2 + 0.19)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.62) - (0.63 - wp.exp(v1 + 0.76)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
